'''Víctor Gustavo Velázquez Ramos''' (born 17 April 1991) is a Paraguayan professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[centre-back]] for [[Cerro Porteño]] and the [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay national team]].

==International career==
Velázquez made his debut for the [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay national team]] on 7 June 2024 in a friendly against [[Peru national football team|Peru]] at [[Estadio Monumental "U"|Estadio Monumental]]. He played the full game which ended in a scoreless draw.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=ESPN|url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/match/_/gameId/701635|title=Peru v Paraguay game report|date=7 June 2024}}</ref>

